Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:09.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Then you also went\Nto the fortune teller Pandora...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.21,0:00:11.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And when I came to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:15.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...the ring, which was\Na family heirloom, was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:17.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's the same trick as the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But, Sister! I'm sure of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:24.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The one who stole\Nthe ring is St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:26.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:33.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,MOM'S ENEMY!\NROSEMARY'S CONSPIRACY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:40.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,SERIAL ROBBERY\NBY SAINT TAIL CONTINUES
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:44.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is the longest\Nit's gone in Seika City's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:50.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that all of the victims\Nare saying St. Tail did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:52.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:55.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What a terrible thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:58.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My dad says\Nhe can't sleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:00.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:06.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that\Nshe would do these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:21.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:23.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A warning note...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:27.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail's warning note\Nhasn't been delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:30.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We had an agreement...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:33.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...that she would give me\Na warning note every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's never broken the promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:39.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:41.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Those newspaper articles...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:43.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:50.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:58.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It has to be hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:01.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All of the victims are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:04.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...made to believe\Nthat St. Tail stole their things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:09.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's the revenge\Non the Mysterious Thief Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,In order to get\Nrevenge on my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:12.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...she's giving me trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:14.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:15.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:19.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Even though I thought it was\Ndisrespectful to your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:23.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...I researched the old articles\Nabout Mysterious Thief Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:29.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:30.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,THIEF LUCIFER PUBLICLY\NCHALLENGES ROSEMARY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:34.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It looks like\NMysterious Thief Lucifer's warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mom. What a showoff...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,In this article, Rosemary...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:43.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...seemed to be Lucifer's\Nopponent, I mean, rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:46.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I heard\Nabout her from Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She was like a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:51.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The person who resents\NLucifer can only be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:52.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...this same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:56.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Mom returned\Nall of the items she had stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:00.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But this Rosemary...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:02.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...has some connection\Nwith that girl...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Pandora again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I may find the location\Nof the victim's ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:15.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Seira,\Nhow do you pronounce this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,FORTUNE TELLING
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If the same thing\Nhappens to me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:40.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But I have to go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,For the sake\Nof St. Tail's reputation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:56.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!\NI've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:57.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,PANDORA'S ORIGINAL GOODS\NMEDUSA CHAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:02.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to be\Nthat surprised! Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mom...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mom! You've got\Nto get rid of that habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:26.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You look exactly like\NLucifer did at that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But cuteness is only skin deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:45.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Lucifer... She loved doing\Nthings that people hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:48.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She always targeted\Nthe item I was planning to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She was like a snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's right! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:55.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that\Nsomewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,AIthough I don't have\Nany grudge against you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...you have to come along with me\Nso that I can get my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:06.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Just curse the fates you were\Nborn as Lucifer's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Kabako...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:12.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,KABA (HIPPOPOTAMUS) KO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:20.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're Ms. Kabako Sendo,\Nalso known as Rosemary, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I learned how to read\Nyour name from Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please don't address me\Nwith my ridiculous real name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:25.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:30.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That horrible\Nwarning note from Lucifer...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:34.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Because of that,\Nthe public knew my real name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...and people made fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:36.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's right! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The humiliation...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:41.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've never, even for a second,\Nforgotten that feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:45.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Like mother, like daughter!\NHow hateful! I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean anything by it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to know\Nabout the theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The stolen items are not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:57.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We don't know anything\Nabout the items St. Tail stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Right, Maju?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Right, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This mother and daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have disturbed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Come back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How infuriating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Who do they think they are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:25.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I checked for places\Nwhere a pair posing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:27.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...as mother and daughter\Nhave moved in recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:29.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is the only place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is a monastery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:35.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's the old building\Nalong the seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's not used now,\Nand it's supposed to be empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's been for sale\Nfor quite a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:44.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But people thought it was creepy\Nand didn't want to get closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:46.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If those two are there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:48.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...the stolen items\Nmust be there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And I'll clear St. Tail's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:59.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of Asuka Jr., too,\Nwho believes in me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:11.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! Someone else\Nmust be using St. Tail's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:15.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She must have been forced to be\Ninvolved in such a strange case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:20.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- That blimp!\N- Something is written on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"Tonight I'm going to the monastery...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...to take the rings and other things\Nwhich are in the possession...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:28.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...of Kabako Sendo,\Nalso known as Rosemary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:29.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:32.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's St. Tail's warning note!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:35.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:42.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I used the same\Nwarning note as my mom's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:44.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're worrying\Nabout the location, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. can figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:51.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:55.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is it wise to show her real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:01.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:04.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I was only thinking about doing\Nthe same thing as my mom did...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:17.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She is indeed\NLucifer's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:20.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She has a lot of guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:23.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter whether\Nit's the mother or daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:28.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Your money's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank... Thank you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:39.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But who is Rosemary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:43.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Her last few messages\Nhave been difficult to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I am Rosemary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:53.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How do you do, Mr. Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:56.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:01.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Rosemary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:12.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is jade dust...\NIt's pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't take your eyes off of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:18.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?\NI can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:42.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about\Nnot understanding what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Cute little detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:47.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm inviting you to my house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:50.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So what are you\Ngoing to do, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Your weak point\Nis now in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:56.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You angered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret it,\Nand you'll wish you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:18.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:24.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:28.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:33.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:00.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:07.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:08.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:10.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:43.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. isn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Nor is his security staff...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't fiind this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:56.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You... didn't come...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:06.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The item you're looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:12.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But no matter\Nhow much you search here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...the detective won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Maju...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:20.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:22.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:24.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You'll see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:58.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't be misled, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:00.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is hypnosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:06.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:08.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:16.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,lllusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She created\Na wind with her magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:36.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...and pushed away\Nmy hypnosis...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:47.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:54.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, weren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:55.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that. Look this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:01.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell who is next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:04.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:09.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is a one-way mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They can't see us\Nfrom the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:14.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You'd better watch\Nclosely from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:17.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...and see what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:35.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:39.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...Show...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:42.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's payback time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:51.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Curtain ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:13.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:18.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:31.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten back\Neverything you stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:37.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:49.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:52.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...that they don't want\Nother people to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:56.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You do, too, daughter of Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:07.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That was loud.\NIt sounds like a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Eimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:12.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There is always an end\Nto everything and every storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:17.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There is an end to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's very near. Watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:45.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll do the same to you, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Until I catch you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:14.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...don't get caught...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:20.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to know\Nher identity, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:40.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're pleased, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:07.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:16.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi!
